{
  "stem": "21611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were people that they paid them, like, potatoes or flour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or people used to change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was our time to change, if you had a good coat [INAUDIBLE] so you changed for food, for potatoes, or-- it wasn't enough food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- there was a Judenrat, and my uncle was in the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, there was the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a name for them was [NON-ENGLISH], because there was [NON-ENGLISH], and there was SS.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] used to-- they arrived to our city demanding all the leather things, and silver, gold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this committee made sure that all of us gave into this place, and they picked it up from there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The SS, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the-- this was the job from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "SS was the killers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew what's going on because they knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- my uncle, we knew from our uncle because he was in the committee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave everybody [? neft ?].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know [? neft ?], yeah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it-- I don't know, [? neft ?].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told the Jewish people, and I'll go out, and they'll shoot me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was two days after Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were three graves already prepared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew there were three graves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it wasn't far from the place I lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he was shot, the Jews started to burn the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did it because we lived not far-- the ghetto was not far from a cemetery, and not far from a forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The forest, the name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Postamit ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he wanted at least somebody should be able to run out and to live through the war, and to tell the horrible things what's happening to us.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
